      </td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
        Careers that focus on working with tools, machines, systems, or physical processes
        <br>
        <img src="https://images.code.org/4f245e227cb52dd6f6793497be3fb313-electrician.png" alt="Things category" style="border-radius:0px; height: 75px; margin: 10px 0;">
      </td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: center;">
        Careers that focus on solving big problems, creativity, and critical thinking
        <br>
